def make_divisors(n):
    lower_div , upper_div = [], []
    i = 1
    while i*i <= n:
        if n % i == 0:
            lower_div.append(i)
            if i != n // i:
                upper_div.append(n//i)
        i += 1
    return lower_div + upper_div[::-1]
